 in purple</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v25_4_5\">embrace ash heaps.</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v25_4_6\"><sup id=\"Lam.4.6\" class=\"v25_4_6\">6</sup>For the chastisement of the daughter of my people has been greater</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v25_4_6\">than the punishment of Sodom,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v25_4_6\">which was overthrown in a moment,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v25_4_6\">and no hands were wrung for her.</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v25_4_7\"><sup id=\"Lam.4.7\" class=\"v25_4_7\">7</sup>Her princes were purer than snow,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v25_4_7\">whiter than milk;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v25_4_7\">their bodies were more ruddy than coral,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v25_4_7\">the beauty of their form was like sapphire.</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v25_4_8\"><sup id=\"Lam.4.8\" class=\"v25_4_8\">8</sup>Now their face is blacker than soot;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v25_4_8\">they are not recognized in the streets;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v25_4_8\">their skin has shriveled on their bones;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v25_4_8\">it has become as dry as wood.</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v25_4_9\"><sup id=\"Lam.4.9\" class=\"v25_4_9\">9</sup>Happier were the victims of the sword</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v25_4_9\">than the victims of hunger,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v25_4_9\">who wasted away, pierced</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v25_4_9\">by lack of the fruits of the field.</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v25_4_10\"><sup id=\"Lam.4.10\" class=\"v25_4_10\">10</sup>The hands of compassionate women</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v25_4_10\">have boiled their own children;</span>